Summary:

    On the groups travels they encounter a lonely building or a fellow traveler. The person has a request for the party, help them locate the remains of their war hero grandfather. They have narrowed their search to a nearby area but it's swarming with some relevant enemy. After a fight the adventurers will find a memorial depicting their grandfather's heroic deeds as well as his hand wraps. He chooses to gift the hand wraps to the party for helping him complete his quest.

    Ideally someone in the party is a hand to hand fighter who will use these hand wraps. 